text: San Lorenzo is a village in Tuscany, central Italy, administratively a frazione of the comune of Suvereto, province of Livorno. At the time of the 2011 census its population was 72. San Lorenzo is about 80 km from Livorno and 5 km from Suvereto. == Bibliography == * == External links == * Category:Frazioni of the Province of Livorno
title: San Lorenzo, Suvereto
